# IndusMind AI — Industrial Knowledge Intelligence Platform

> **"The AI Brain for Industrial Operations"**

Complete architecture, database schema, API design, and phased development roadmap for an enterprise-grade AI platform that transforms industrial document chaos into structured, actionable intelligence.

