## API Design

### Base URL: `/api/v1`

### Authentication
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/auth/verify` | Verify Clerk JWT, create/sync user |
| `GET` | `/auth/me` | Get current user profile |
| `PUT` | `/auth/me` | Update user profile |

### Documents
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/documents/upload` | Upload document(s) — multipart |
| `GET` | `/documents` | List documents (paginated, filterable) |
| `GET` | `/documents/{id}` | Get document detail + metadata |
| `GET` | `/documents/{id}/preview` | Get document preview / extracted text |
| `GET` | `/documents/{id}/chunks` | Get document chunks |
| `DELETE` | `/documents/{id}` | Delete document + associated data |
| `PATCH` | `/documents/{id}` | Update tags, category, metadata |
| `GET` | `/documents/{id}/status` | Get processing status |

### AI Chat
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/chat/conversations` | Create new conversation |
| `GET` | `/chat/conversations` | List user conversations |
| `GET` | `/chat/conversations/{id}` | Get conversation with messages |
| `DELETE` | `/chat/conversations/{id}` | Delete conversation |
| `POST` | `/chat/conversations/{id}/messages` | Send message, get AI response |
| `WS` | `/chat/ws/{conversation_id}` | WebSocket for streaming responses |

### Knowledge Graph
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/knowledge-graph` | Get full graph (nodes + edges) |
| `GET` | `/knowledge-graph/nodes` | List nodes (filterable by type) |
| `GET` | `/knowledge-graph/nodes/{id}` | Get node with relationships |
| `GET` | `/knowledge-graph/search` | Search graph by entity name |
| `GET` | `/knowledge-graph/stats` | Graph statistics |

### Equipment
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/equipment` | List all equipment |
| `GET` | `/equipment/{id}` | Equipment detail with history |
| `POST` | `/equipment` | Create equipment record |
| `PUT` | `/equipment/{id}` | Update equipment |
| `GET` | `/equipment/{id}/health` | AI-generated health assessment |

### Maintenance Intelligence
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/maintenance` | List maintenance records |
| `POST` | `/maintenance` | Create maintenance record |
| `GET` | `/maintenance/{id}` | Get maintenance detail |
| `GET` | `/maintenance/intelligence` | AI maintenance insights |
| `GET` | `/maintenance/predictions` | Failure predictions (simulated) |
| `GET` | `/maintenance/overdue` | Overdue maintenance items |

### Compliance Intelligence
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/compliance` | List compliance records |
| `POST` | `/compliance/analyze` | Run compliance analysis on document |
| `GET` | `/compliance/score` | Overall compliance score |
| `GET` | `/compliance/violations` | Active violations |
| `GET` | `/compliance/audit-summary` | AI-generated audit summary |

### Analytics
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/analytics/dashboard` | Dashboard summary cards |
| `GET` | `/analytics/incidents` | Incident trends |
| `GET` | `/analytics/equipment-health` | Equipment health rankings |
| `GET` | `/analytics/compliance-trend` | Compliance trend over time |
| `GET` | `/analytics/maintenance-trend` | Maintenance trend |
| `GET` | `/analytics/document-growth` | Document ingestion over time |

### Search
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/search` | Global semantic + keyword search |
| `GET` | `/search/semantic` | Pure vector similarity search |
| `GET` | `/search/filters` | Available filter options |

